{"tid":1632660,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"裝修都可以俾國際社會接受","createTime":"2019-10-06T19:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:08:53.000Z","uid":80972,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fc3d27c5da642594f2e0203458007cce1b780e1e","tid":1632660,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:30:32.000Z","msg":"從來起兵用動武都有條件同理由<br />\n<br />\n鶳就係人地先用武，我地先以武止暴<br />\n<br />\n除左藍罷買，紅裝修外，我地都為裝修加入更明確嘅理由<br />\n<br />\nPopo開1槍(海綿/布袋) = 爆1間鋪<br />\nPopo開實1槍實彈 = 爆5間鋪<br />\n<br />\n因為首先暴力嘅係狗隊，我覺得大家開始連實彈都麻木! 我地裝修係應該帶出<span style=\"color: orange;\">以牙還牙，以暴還暴，用<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">行動抗議警暴</span></span>!<br />\n<br />\n爆完間鋪，大大隻字寫返以暴還暴，最好拎埋粒射完嘅海綿彈塞入牆度做文宣，<span style=\"color: red;\">一鋪一彈</span>。<br />\n<br />\n如果狗隊唔出爆力武器，我地先會考慮停止裝修囉。"},{"pid":"3ec915a931b3f72be513470a971b451f47fb4233","tid":1632660,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:32:02.000Z","msg":"［分化收皮］香港01分化民陣失敗，聲稱裝修過火、民意逆轉<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632454</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8216a7c0786f515005b37061321adcc65d888942","tid":1632660,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:32:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c0d28a9e00f9fae393929b2b204780002174e54","tid":1632660,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:32:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5d378ba31d37389d5fd5f2c9045406220ff6557b","tid":1632660,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:33:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bf3d96771dc894baf66f784ab3850d1a7ee76f85","tid":1632660,"uid":80972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:33:21.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6d81108df10cc921c3b78634e96692b40d07cfc7","tid":1632660,"uid":47149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T19:34:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kis